# Invalid Function Syntax

These function calls should FAIL to parse or evaluate.

## Empty Arguments

avg()

This should fail: avg() requires at least one argument.

## Wrong Argument Count

sqrt()
sqrt(1, 2)

sqrt() expects exactly 1 argument, not 0 or 2.

## Missing Parentheses

avg 1, 2, 3

Traditional syntax requires parentheses.

## Incomplete Natural Language

average 1, 2, 3
average of
square root
square root 16

Natural language requires complete phrase.

## Invalid Function Names

unknown(1, 2)
calculate(10)
